{"id": "ChIJFRPLvtvbwoAR2uii7d1tDck", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 95, "displayName": {"text": "Auntea Jenny (San Gabriel)", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJFRPLvtvbwoAR2uii7d1tDck/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOR2JWcGtRMnBaTFRGUWIwWjVkRlpPZVRoUkxWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This was my first time at Auntea Jenny. I tried their matcha series and it was so rich & creamy. Their tea has a nice fragrant flavor. The store was beautiful decorated, this location is an express shop to grab drinks. The store is pretty small but perfect for grab and go. The workers were super friendly. I would come back to try more of their tea drinks.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This was my first time at Auntea Jenny. I tried their matcha series and it was so rich & creamy. Their tea has a nice fragrant flavor. The store was beautiful decorated, this location is an express shop to grab drinks. The store is pretty small but perfect for grab and go. The workers were super friendly. I would come back to try more of their tea drinks.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "tina tran", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104854631110512620728/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIamWuluu0tE1LFqgKeqf2byMxHW3qjGiUVGJTYQc1Z1rP8Sw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-13T03:08:36.530967791Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOR2JWcGtRMnBaTFRGUWIwWjVkRlpPZVRoUkxWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOR2JWcGtRMnBaTFRGUWIwWjVkRlpPZVRoUkxWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbdbbecb1315:0xc90d6dddeda2e8da"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFRPLvtvbwoAR2uii7d1tDck/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2swek1sWjNPR3hOWlZoQmNHbHRSVkpCVUVOd2FIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Auntea Jenny in San Gabriel offers a solid, creative menu that stands out from standard boba shops, particularly through their focus on unique textures and premium teas. The service here is wonderful, and I loved the classic ambiance of the place.\n\nHere is a breakdown of the drinks ordered:\n\n* Premium Matcha Daifuku Cheese Foam: This is the standout of the group. The inclusion of a stretchy, chewy daifuku texture makes it feel like a liquid dessert. The savory-sweet cheese foam complements the earthiness of the matcha well without overpowering it.\n* Premium Matcha Jasmine Tea Latte: A cleaner, more traditional option. The earthy matcha layers nicely over the floral notes of the jasmine tea, making it a very balanced, refreshing choice if you want something less rich than the daifuku.\n* Classic Mango Pomelo Sago: A well-executed version of the traditional dessert. It is creamy, rich, and filled with a generous amount of mango and pomelo pulp. It leans more toward a dessert than a drink.\n* Lemon Jasmine Tea Punch: Crisp and straightforward. The citrus flavor is sharp and natural, blending well with the jasmine base. It works perfectly as a palate cleanser.\n* Black Sesame Milk Tea with Boba and Grains: Hearty and nutty. The black sesame flavor tastes authentic rather than artificial or powdery. The addition of grains gives it a textured, porridge-like satisfaction, and the boba had a great, consistent chew.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Auntea Jenny in San Gabriel offers a solid, creative menu that stands out from standard boba shops, particularly through their focus on unique textures and premium teas. The service here is wonderful, and I loved the classic ambiance of the place.\n\nHere is a breakdown of the drinks ordered:\n\n* Premium Matcha Daifuku Cheese Foam: This is the standout of the group. The inclusion of a stretchy, chewy daifuku texture makes it feel like a liquid dessert. The savory-sweet cheese foam complements the earthiness of the matcha well without overpowering it.\n* Premium Matcha Jasmine Tea Latte: A cleaner, more traditional option. The earthy matcha layers nicely over the floral notes of the jasmine tea, making it a very balanced, refreshing choice if you want something less rich than the daifuku.\n* Classic Mango Pomelo Sago: A well-executed version of the traditional dessert. It is creamy, rich, and filled with a generous amount of mango and pomelo pulp. It leans more toward a dessert than a drink.\n* Lemon Jasmine Tea Punch: Crisp and straightforward. The citrus flavor is sharp and natural, blending well with the jasmine base. It works perfectly as a palate cleanser.\n* Black Sesame Milk Tea with Boba and Grains: Hearty and nutty. The black sesame flavor tastes authentic rather than artificial or powdery. The addition of grains gives it a textured, porridge-like satisfaction, and the boba had a great, consistent chew.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Allison Wibowo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115077742334432266523/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUGTb6rqEEQq_d-YzWhwr0qQeMkPSi8corLTbQc_ogTZdCBxVSEg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-18T21:39:45.101064946Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2swek1sWjNPR3hOWlZoQmNHbHRSVkpCVUVOd2FIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2swek1sWjNPR3hOWlZoQmNHbHRSVkpCVUVOd2FIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbdbbecb1315:0xc90d6dddeda2e8da"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFRPLvtvbwoAR2uii7d1tDck/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paVGFGRnZPSGxwU1RadFIwZEdXaTFwYm5Fd1FXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I had a wonderful experience at the Auntea Jenny store in San Gabriel. I have visited other locations, and I'm glad I continued to have a good experience here. The staff were very welcoming and accommodating, and it didn't take too long for my drinks to be made. I enjoyed their new matcha series, but the most I enjoyed the superfood drink series- I loved the kale apple! I'd definitely come back to visit if I'm ever in the area", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I had a wonderful experience at the Auntea Jenny store in San Gabriel. I have visited other locations, and I'm glad I continued to have a good experience here. The staff were very welcoming and accommodating, and it didn't take too long for my drinks to be made. I enjoyed their new matcha series, but the most I enjoyed the superfood drink series- I loved the kale apple! I'd definitely come back to visit if I'm ever in the area", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Claire Malley", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108168768709855015581/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0J-13r3wnzWCgrobeAlSji77W6OBvxYJdjBMFpD0CUBVFdg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-13T21:01:54.711309657Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paVGFGRnZPSGxwU1RadFIwZEdXaTFwYm5Fd1FXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paVGFGRnZPSGxwU1RadFIwZEdXaTFwYm5Fd1FXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbdbbecb1315:0xc90d6dddeda2e8da"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFRPLvtvbwoAR2uii7d1tDck/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsRFpsQnhWMnhETm5KMVNWUk9ORlZLVFU5eFYyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I loved the Kale Apple Fiber Chia Seed Boost Tea!\nI usually don’t like kale drinks, but this one didn’t have a strong kale flavor at all. It was delicious, refreshing, and felt like a healthier option that’s great for your skin.\n\nI also loved the White Champaca Oolong Tea Latte! It was my first time trying a white champaca flavor, and it reminded me of a floral perfume. If you enjoy floral flavors like lavender, I think you’ll love this one too.\n\nAnd the boba was perfectly chewy! Highly recommend trying it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I loved the Kale Apple Fiber Chia Seed Boost Tea!\nI usually don’t like kale drinks, but this one didn’t have a strong kale flavor at all. It was delicious, refreshing, and felt like a healthier option that’s great for your skin.\n\nI also loved the White Champaca Oolong Tea Latte! It was my first time trying a white champaca flavor, and it reminded me of a floral perfume. If you enjoy floral flavors like lavender, I think you’ll love this one too.\n\nAnd the boba was perfectly chewy! Highly recommend trying it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "erika", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103377816022693318403/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsiN45N40gnhGlcSGJl2pPNOhDPg7f6eaiwtcneg8XNklS9f4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-30T08:32:39.947011948Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsRFpsQnhWMnhETm5KMVNWUk9ORlZLVFU5eFYyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsRFpsQnhWMnhETm5KMVNWUk9ORlZLVFU5eFYyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbdbbecb1315:0xc90d6dddeda2e8da"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFRPLvtvbwoAR2uii7d1tDck/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psSVgwOWFNMVI1U1dkQlppMW5RMUp4WVcxTkxWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Auntea jenny is located inside a busy plaza but their is a parking structure underneath. The place has one table and a seating area. More of a take out place lots of people seem to place online orders. I had their matcha series and if you are lactose intolerant definitely bring lactaid their milk is real milky. I enjoyed it at 70% sweet which was still sweet to my liking. The boba here is really good perfectly chewy!! They have other drinks like mango sago and their signature glutinous rice milk tea.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Auntea jenny is located inside a busy plaza but their is a parking structure underneath. The place has one table and a seating area. More of a take out place lots of people seem to place online orders. I had their matcha series and if you are lactose intolerant definitely bring lactaid their milk is real milky. I enjoyed it at 70% sweet which was still sweet to my liking. The boba here is really good perfectly chewy!! They have other drinks like mango sago and their signature glutinous rice milk tea.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kat lama", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102923902671161717184/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoVbIXsSnp7mIeYX8PunS5RfkBXRHr89y6411FA_hLt4ZnRA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T03:49:14.364571012Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psSVgwOWFNMVI1U1dkQlppMW5RMUp4WVcxTkxWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psSVgwOWFNMVI1U1dkQlppMW5RMUp4WVcxTkxWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbdbbecb1315:0xc90d6dddeda2e8da"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJFRPLvtvbwoAR2uii7d1tDck/photos/AWCwydgTES37iR52A7nGLcTwmy8qJHJnPQk0eoy8ud5mcaqJvhCZqSgEeizH51YnxBnh6iHyqE0WHQnuRT1YbNWUlfIzusCwoye2qdJV90zSKrDquHA51h9m0y_FSE6ogX209ZE9bHL5KAXHl4ZPphAP3_g8fjIG--mU1kV4MXciQn0WG2xpVv_4bnailjm4K2VrVuMzf2si41DBYM4Tu7kerRdU9sgoGH_97elZzWmGlYOfRtdACZMqKgfCNoUKp7KwIY4PDXVXXo51EGP6qTyh9_Br2BPOsJJrok1nm6qyb3wGXb_XP_7SjUkOeQe2Pn_5thYqVZ5dqn3mMUtYwo0-gn4wbYHOwv7EYrT7bA1k-6QCczdNifW3ExLBhgSqvPw2qYDNE5HdyrVCpD5io6p50bO9DNa8wxz8Tv_xnkvwMfJR6RYZjmUn2xnr3n5FcC94", "widthPx": 1290, "heightPx": 1583, "authorAttributions": [{"displayNam